# Arch AUR packages — NOT signed/vetted like the official repos.
# These are installed via yay with mandatory PKGBUILD review (see SECURITY.md
# and `archy-aur-notice`). Every entry below was verified (2026-06) to be an
# actively-maintained package pulling from its genuine, official upstream:
#
#   helium-browser-bin   imputnet/helium-linux releases (PGP-verified)
#   walker-bin           github.com/abenz1267/walker (upstream author)
#   elephant-all-bin     github.com/abenz1267/elephant (walker data providers)
#   slack-desktop        slack.com/downloads
#   onlyoffice-bin       onlyoffice.com
#   1password            downloads.1password.com (vendor-maintained, signed)
#   1password-cli        cache.agilebits.com (1Password's company)
#   localsend-bin        github.com/localsend/localsend releases
#   python-terminaltexteffects  PyPI (screensaver engine)
#   tzupdate             github.com/cdown/tzupdate
#   ufw-docker           github.com/chaifeng/ufw-docker
#   xdg-terminal-exec    freedesktop xdg-terminal-exec spec impl
#   yaru-icon-theme      Ubuntu Yaru icons

